name: 30 Second Toy Delivery
description:
YOU WORK FOR A TOY HEAD DELIVERY SERVICE. YOU ARE TASKED WITH DELIVERING SPECIFIC HEADS TO PEOPLE IN A LIMITED AMOUNT OF TIME. TRY YOUR BEST NOT TO FAIL. 

Choose the correct toy head using your mouse. Failure to correctly choose the head will result in a time deficit. So choose carefully. 

This game was made in under 6 hours for fun. :>
